name: Cheese On Wheels Cel Animation
description:
Single Edition
Cel-Animation 
By: Dave Gamez
1080px x 1080px/mp4

This is the hand-drawn animated version of my beloved character "Cheese On Wheels" which was the starting point for the versions that are now sold as NFTs, there's a whole lot of love put into this project and I'm glad I could take a character from sketch into three different technics of animation.
